                  <rs id="t18800322-343-offence-2" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18800322-343-offence-2" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18800322-343-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>, Feloniously aiding and abetting her in the same.</rs>
